episodes.title: Exposing a New Christian Modern Cult | Part 2 Trish's Background Story of Abuse
episodes.description:
Heys guys - so there is a new cult going around it fairly new and modern and they prey of vulnerable people. For Trish and Maka, we both had a history of abuse which made us more impressionable. 

This background story is necessary in helping you understand why we were easily influence by this predator.
